o-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-wwxs7iJe3IRK6mSsXfh_gQ">Thảo đường - 草堂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1i-T%E1%BB%95/Th%C3%A2n-chinh-Ph%E1%BB%A5c-L%E1%BB%85-ch%C3%A2u-%C4%90i%C3%AAu-C%C3%A1t-H%C3%A3n/poem-8Mir9LSQnbD8RpS-vSvfgw">Thân chinh Phục Lễ châu Điêu Cát Hãn - 親征復禮州刁吉罕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1i-T%E1%BB%95/author-2yzXyHJUmXU_0XKOwM--LA">Lê Thái Tổ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-Vi-Ph%C3%BAng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-L%C3%A3ng-Ch%C3%A2u-l%E1%BB%A5c-s%E1%BB%B1-tham-qu%C3%A2n/poem-OWVAemeEA6UazTOSnqx8sg">Tống Vi Phúng thướng Lãng Châu lục sự tham quân - 送韋諷上閬州錄事參軍</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BB%AD-Hy-Nhan/Tr%E1%BA%A3m-x%C3%A0-ki%E1%BA%BFm-ph%C3%BA/poem-4mnvnyA6k6RfA2JMT5OVyQ">Trảm xà kiếm phú - 斬蛇劍賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BB%AD-Hy-Nhan/author-_3sTvaRn7XDoRGq_884L9Q">Sử Hy Nhan</a>)<br></div>	</div>
